ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 457.00 Tm
(level. The same technical failure may have very different consequences at each level.) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 441.00 Tm
(A measurable impact of AI system failure is often financial cost, such as the cost created) Tj
