BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 528.00 Tm
(best when features are scaled and K is chosen carefully.) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 512.00 Tm
